    "headline": "ADM appoints Michael McMurray to its Board of Directors.",
    "narrative_summary": "Archer-Daniels-Midland Company announced the appointment of Michael C. McMurray as an independent director to its Board, effective March 9, 2026. McMurray brings over three decades of financial and strategic leadership experience from companies like LyondellBasell, Owens Corning, and Royal Dutch Shell. He will serve on the Audit and Sustainability and Technology Committees."
